446
00:22:30,280 --> 00:22:31,830
You have to take over the position

447
00:22:32,190 --> 00:22:33,590
of Minister of the Ministry of Revenue.

448
00:22:35,160 --> 00:22:38,040
So does Fan Xian with his visit.

449
00:22:39,590 --> 00:22:40,400
Your Majesty!

450
00:22:40,470 --> 00:22:41,520
No bargaining!

451
00:22:45,800 --> 00:22:47,470
Then please allow my personal guards

452
00:22:48,070 --> 00:22:49,830
