519
00:26:00,160 --> 00:26:02,000
If it ever happens again,

520
00:26:02,950 --> 00:26:05,110
there can't be any mistakes.

521
00:26:07,680 --> 00:26:08,920
So the shop sustains.

522
00:26:09,880 --> 00:26:10,590
For many years?

