I heard that

569
00:28:12,880 --> 00:28:14,590
you're going to escort Xiao En to Beiqi.

570
00:28:14,760 --> 00:28:15,470
Yes.

571
00:28:15,950 --> 00:28:16,950
To get Yan Bingyun back.

572
00:28:17,040 --> 00:28:18,430
Which jerk comes up with such a lousy idea?

573
00:28:19,560 --> 00:28:20,230
Don't go!

574
00:28:20,830 --> 00:28:23,230
It is His Majesty's idea.

575
00:28:29,640 --> 00:28:31,400
You must flee from the capital city.

576
00:28:33,590 --> 00:28:34,430
Get prepared.

577
00:28:34,760 --> 00:28:35,760
We set out tonight.

578
00:28:35,760 --> 00:28:36,400
Teacher!

579
00:28:38,760 --> 00:28:41,280
Xiao En deeply hates the Investigator's Office.

580
00:28:41,590 --> 00:28:43,520
We can't hold back the relationship

581
00:28:43,520 --> 00:28:44,800
between you and me or Chen Pingping from him.

582
00:28:46,400 --> 00:28:47,310
How will you cope with Xiao En

583
00:28:47,950 --> 00:28:48,920
after you get to Beiqi?

584
00:28:49,230 --> 00:28:50,430
Teacher, I can manage it.

585
00:28:50,590 --> 00:28:51,470
Just listen to me on this.

586
00:28:53,880 --> 00:28:54,880
Leave tonight.

587
00:28:56,040 --> 00:28:57,560
I'll sort out the route of fleeing.

588
00:28:59,160 --> 00:28:59,640
No!

589
00:28:59,640 --> 00:29:00,640
Mr. Fei, how about me?

590
00:29:00,640 --> 00:29:01,350
Wait for us.

591
00:29:02,110 --> 00:29:03,110
Flee with us together at dusk.

592
00:29:03,560 --> 00:29:04,070
No,

593
00:29:04,070 --> 00:29:05,430
my wife and daughter

594
00:29:05,430 --> 00:29:06,640
are all in the capital city.

595
00:29:09,110 --> 00:29:10,520
What does that have to do with me?

596
00:29:10,760 --> 00:29:11,470
Teacher,

597
00:29:11,590 --> 00:29:12,640
neither the Investigator's Office

598
00:29:12,640 --> 00:29:13,640
nor the Imperial Guards will let me go!

599
00:29:17,310 --> 00:29:18,520
I'll kill

600
00:29:18,560 --> 00:29:20,000
whoever stands in our way.

601
00:29:25,830 --> 00:29:26,680
Including me?

602
00:29:27,800 --> 00:29:28,800
How do you know this place?

603
00:29:29,280 --> 00:29:30,400
I know it all the time.

604
00:29:37,070 --> 00:29:38,230
Fan Xian can't go to Beiqi.

605
00:29:38,520 --> 00:29:41,000
You know the consequence to act against the imperial edict.

606
00:29:42,310 --> 00:29:43,560
If Fan Xian flees,

607
00:29:44,070 --> 00:29:44,800
he will have no ground to stand in Nanqing

608
00:29:44,800 --> 00:29:47,160
for the rest of his life.

609
00:29:48,350 --> 00:29:50,310
That's not any worse than dying in Beiqi.

610
00:29:50,430 --> 00:29:51,280
So what?

611
00:29:51,680 --> 00:29:52,950
You want him to be like you

612
00:29:53,040 --> 00:29:54,110
who travels around the world

613
00:29:54,160 --> 00:29:54,880
and never be able to see

614
00:29:54,880 --> 00:29:56,000
families or friends?

615
00:29:56,230 --> 00:29:57,430
I am old.

616
00:29:58,470 --> 00:30:00,230
Over all the years I've spent in the Investigator's Office,

617
00:30:00,470 --> 00:30:01,040
I've seen enough of this type

618
00:30:01,040 --> 00:30:02,560
of life and death farewell.

619
00:30:02,920 --> 00:30:04,640
I can't watch him dying.

620
00:30:14,800 --> 00:30:15,710
Besides,

621
00:30:17,040 --> 00:30:18,110
after I die,

622
00:30:19,760 --> 00:30:21,280
there is gotta be someone burying me.

623
00:30:23,190 --> 00:30:24,160
I can't find anyone else

624
00:30:25,800 --> 00:30:27,280
other than Fan Xian.

625
00:30:32,040 --> 00:30:33,880
If only one person can live in the world,

626
00:30:34,520 --> 00:30:36,400
I will surely choose Fan Xian.

627
00:30:37,070 --> 00:30:38,230
Then why do you let him

628
00:30:38,590 --> 00:30:40,760
escort Xiao En to Beiqi?

629
00:30:46,000 --> 00:30:47,230
Do you know?

630
00:30:47,680 --> 00:30:48,640
After he comes back this time,

631
00:30:50,430 --> 00:30:51,470
the future of the capital city

632
00:30:51,470 --> 00:30:53,160
will all be in his hands.

633
00:30:53,310 --> 00:30:55,160
That's too dangerous, Head Chen.

634
00:30:55,230 --> 00:30:57,560
Whose life isn't dangerous?

635
00:30:58,070 --> 00:30:58,760
If he shall live

636
00:30:58,760 --> 00:30:59,680
under your shadow and mine,

637
00:30:59,680 --> 00:31:00,590
he'll be ruined.

638
00:31:00,590 --> 00:31:01,830
Don't worry!

639
00:31:01,830 --> 00:31:03,640
I'll ensure his safety.

640
00:31:03,830 --> 00:31:04,680
Stand up!

641
00:31:05,310 --> 00:31:06,680
I'll trust you if you stand up now.

642
00:31:07,640 --> 00:31:08,920
It was because of me back then

643
00:31:10,160 --> 00:31:11,880
that you lost your legs.

644
00:31:18,640 --> 00:31:19,430
Your Excellency!

645
00:31:22,000 --> 00:31:22,680
Teacher,

646
00:31:23,560 --> 00:31:24,710
I'm willing to go to Beiqi.

647
00:31:27,230 --> 00:31:28,520
Li Yunrui betrayed Yan Bingyun

648
00:31:28,950 --> 00:31:30,040
to destroy me.

649
00:31:30,710 --> 00:31:32,000
I'm the cause of it.

650
00:31:32,830 --> 00:31:34,190
So I have to get him back.

651
00:32:18,920 --> 00:32:20,070
So beautiful!

652
00:32:35,560 --> 00:32:36,920
Didn't you say

653
00:32:37,000 --> 00:32:38,040
you have important things to tell me?

654
00:32:38,560 --> 00:32:39,760
Why don't you talk?

655
00:32:42,400 --> 00:32:43,520
I'm going to Beiqi.

656
00:32:44,520 --> 00:32:45,400
I know.

657
00:32:46,950 --> 00:32:47,950
Actually, I don't want to go.

658
00:32:48,070 --> 00:32:48,880
Then don't!

659
00:32:54,400 --> 00:32:55,680
The worse result is to disappoint His Majesty's will

660
00:32:56,000 --> 00:32:57,160
and go back to Danzhou with you.

661
00:33:01,350 --> 00:33:02,760
If I don't go to Beiqi,

662
00:33:04,310 --> 00:33:07,280
the marriage contract will be gone.

663
00:33:08,400 --> 00:33:09,520
That's the idea of His Majesty?

664
00:33:11,350 --> 00:33:12,560
Who else's could it be?

665
00:33:14,280 --> 00:33:15,760
We can elope.

666
00:33:26,950 --> 00:33:28,470
I've saved up a little bit of money.

667
00:33:28,680 --> 00:33:30,190
If we keep ourselves frugal,

668
00:33:30,190 --> 00:33:31,430
it's enough for our whole lives.

669
00:33:33,280 --> 00:33:35,110
The only thing is the Investigator's Office may come after us.

670
00:33:36,230 --> 00:33:37,160
How about

671
00:33:38,470 --> 00:33:39,470
going out on the sea?

672
00:33:39,590 --> 00:33:42,190
Set out on sail with a large boat.

673
00:33:42,190 --> 00:33:43,560
We stop at wherever it goes

674
00:33:43,710 --> 00:33:44,430
until no one

675
00:33:44,430 --> 00:33:45,800
can find us.

676
00:33:46,640 --> 00:33:47,560
Setting out on sail

677
00:33:47,830 --> 00:33:48,880
means never being able to come back.

678
00:33:49,190 --> 00:33:49,880
Aren't you afraid?

679
00:33:50,470 --> 00:33:53,160
You will protect me, right?

680
00:34:05,520 --> 00:34:07,640
You're too adorable. I couldn't hold it.

681
00:34:10,120 --> 00:34:11,760
I'm serious.

682
00:34:14,520 --> 00:34:15,670
If you elope with me,

683
00:34:17,360 --> 00:34:18,470
do you know how many people will laugh at you?

684
00:34:18,710 --> 00:34:19,360
I don't care.

685
00:34:19,360 --> 00:34:20,120
I do!

686
00:34:22,710 --> 00:34:23,560
Wait for me to come back.

687
00:34:25,190 --> 00:34:26,470
After I come back from Beiqi,

688
00:34:27,190 --> 00:34:28,190
let's get married.

689
00:34:35,630 --> 00:34:37,230
I don't want you

690
00:34:37,600 --> 00:34:38,630
to force yourself

691
00:34:39,360 --> 00:34:41,040
into something you don't like for me.

692
00:34:41,190 --> 00:34:42,000
Not at all.

693
00:34:44,040 --> 00:34:45,670
Knowing that we can get married after I come back,

694
00:34:45,910 --> 00:34:47,230
I wish I could set out tonight.

695
00:34:48,760 --> 00:34:50,280
Aren't you afraid of being watched?

696
00:34:50,360 --> 00:34:51,000
No!

697
00:34:51,600 --> 00:34:52,600
I've sent them away.

698
00:34:53,280 --> 00:34:54,230
You sent them away?

699
00:34:58,520 --> 00:35:00,320
So you did plan it.

700
00:35:00,950 --> 00:35:01,760
Come on! I'm about to leave.

701
00:35:02,600 --> 00:35:04,040
Take it as a farewell gift.

702
00:35:04,040 --> 00:35:06,120
Wait! Stand straight.

703
00:35:07,870 --> 00:35:09,600
Put your hands at the back and don't move.

704
00:35:12,120 --> 00:35:13,230
We must agree on three points of law.

705
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:16,760
Firstly, don't flirt with any other ladies in Beiqi.

706
00:35:17,360 --> 00:35:18,870
No one but you would accept me.

707
00:35:19,000 --> 00:35:20,230
What if there is someone?

708
00:35:21,630 --> 00:35:23,950
I accept no one but you.

709
00:35:36,190 --> 00:35:37,600
I couldn't hold it.

710
00:35:47,910 --> 00:35:49,080
Why do you laugh?

711
00:35:49,080 --> 00:35:50,150
No, I don't.

712
00:35:50,190 --> 00:35:51,760
I couldn't help enjoying the aftertaste.

713
00:36:00,840 --> 00:36:02,230
You said three points of law.

714
00:36:02,600 --> 00:36:03,470
So what are the rest two points?

715
00:36:06,040 --> 00:36:07,320
I haven't come up yet.

716
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:09,670
No worries. Take your time.

717
00:36:10,150 --> 00:36:11,120
What are you doing?

718
00:36:11,600 --> 00:36:12,430
I miss you already.

719
00:36:12,520 --> 00:36:13,630
You haven't left yet.

720
00:36:13,870 --> 00:36:14,950
I start to miss you even before I leave.

721
00:36:15,710 --> 00:36:17,120
Fine, but hold you mouth back from me.

722
00:36:20,040 --> 00:36:21,670
Sure, whatever you say.

723
00:36:26,670 --> 00:36:28,080
Listen to me carefully.

724
00:36:30,000 --> 00:36:31,520
You must come back alive

725
00:36:32,910 --> 00:36:34,390
from this journey.

726
00:36:36,840 --> 00:36:38,320
I'll be waiting for you here

727
00:36:40,800 --> 00:36:42,190
with cherry flowers.

728
00:37:56,870 --> 00:37:57,910
Xie Bi'an

729
00:37:58,280 --> 00:37:59,190
is not only good sword

730
00:37:59,190 --> 00:38:00,600
but also a scary one.

731
00:38:03,520 --> 00:38:04,670
Let him in.

732
00:38:14,080 --> 00:38:15,150
You sent Wan'er back?

733
00:38:15,280 --> 00:38:16,950
I don't remember having such pavilion before.

734
00:38:17,360 --> 00:38:17,950
Just built it.

735
00:38:18,710 --> 00:38:19,470
Watch out!

736
00:38:20,600 --> 00:38:21,560
There is no base!

737
00:38:21,760 --> 00:38:22,800
This will be removed after the drink.

738
00:38:27,390 --> 00:38:28,520
This is just for a drink?

739
00:38:31,280 --> 00:38:32,430
You can't leave me waiting

740
00:38:32,520 --> 00:38:34,600
in the middle of the road, right?

741
00:38:34,950 --> 00:38:36,520
So I built this pavilion.

742
00:38:39,600 --> 00:38:40,670
Why do you look at me like that?

743
00:38:41,280 --> 00:38:42,430
As a prince,

744
00:38:42,950 --> 00:38:44,280
wouldn't it be a breach of duty

745
00:38:45,840 --> 00:38:47,280
if I don't live extravagantly?

746
00:38:48,870 --> 00:38:50,600
That makes sense.

747
00:38:54,840 --> 00:38:55,950
A toast to you.

748
00:39:02,840 --> 00:39:03,470
Good liquor.

749
00:39:06,120 --> 00:39:07,230
Is it?

750
00:39:09,800 --> 00:39:10,910
With the support of this scenery,

751
00:39:11,230 --> 00:39:12,360
any liquor can be good.

752
00:39:16,230 --> 00:39:17,080
When do you set out?

753
00:39:17,710 --> 00:39:18,560
In a couple of days.

754
00:39:20,950 --> 00:39:22,320
When you come back,

755
00:39:22,600 --> 00:39:24,120
you'll enjoy enviable reputation.

756
00:39:25,320 --> 00:39:27,190
By then, the imperial examinations
held in spring will start soon.

757
00:39:28,470 --> 00:39:29,760
I'll plead His Majesty

758
00:39:31,800 --> 00:39:33,000
to appoint you as the examiner.

759
00:39:34,840 --> 00:39:36,280
I don't have any reputation.

760
00:39:38,520 --> 00:39:40,080
The title of the Poetic Genius Fan is enough.

761
00:39:41,360 --> 00:39:43,320
Once you organize the imperial examinations held in spring,

762
00:39:44,190 --> 00:39:47,190
you'll become the examiner of those students.

763
00:39:47,710 --> 00:39:49,190
It's hard to fully describe

764
00:39:49,560 --> 00:39:51,040
the advantages behind it.

765
00:39:51,950 --> 00:39:53,000
Feel it yourself.

766
00:39:54,430 --> 00:39:55,280
I'm just curious

767
00:39:56,000 --> 00:39:57,000
