768
00:39:57,670 --> 00:39:59,230
to me.

769
00:40:07,800 --> 00:40:08,710
You're not hateful

770
00:40:08,950 --> 00:40:10,150
and can drink with me together.

771
00:40:11,390 --> 00:40:14,000
Even if you follow the Crown Prince in the end,

772
00:40:15,910 --> 00:40:17,390
we can still be friends.

773
00:40:20,000 --> 00:40:21,230
Your Highness is most generous.

774
00:40:32,800 --> 00:40:34,800
This world is full of common people.

775
00:40:35,800 --> 00:40:37,520
There aren't many people

776
00:40:38,760 --> 00:40:40,000
with whom you can open your heart.

777
00:40:40,840 --> 00:40:42,080
I've read your poems.

778
00:40:44,320 --> 00:40:47,390
"The capital city has so many officials.

779
00:40:48,430 --> 00:40:51,760
Only this one guy looks frustrated and unhappy."

780
00:40:52,360 --> 00:40:53,840
There are certain sincerity behind it.

781
00:41:02,600 --> 00:41:04,360
There are a lot of routes to the north.

782
00:41:05,630 --> 00:41:08,360
The guardian at Fengming Pass is my follower.

783
00:41:08,710 --> 00:41:10,360
If you go through there, I'll ask him to protect you.

784
00:41:11,230 --> 00:41:12,040
Thank you,

785
00:41:12,520 --> 00:41:13,630
but we probably won't go through Fengming

786
00:41:13,630 --> 00:41:14,760
this time.

787
00:41:15,320 --> 00:41:16,430
Because it's a long route.

788
00:41:17,710 --> 00:41:18,560
Then forget about it.

789
00:41:18,840 --> 00:41:21,280
The feast is over and now it's time to move apart.

790
00:41:22,120 --> 00:41:23,630
It is a pretty good day.

791
00:41:23,950 --> 00:41:25,600
I'll wait for your return.

792
00:41:28,190 --> 00:41:29,000
See you!

793
00:42:12,560 --> 00:42:14,040
Don't tell anyone

794
00:42:14,360 --> 00:42:15,800
about which pass you'll go through

795
00:42:16,120 --> 00:42:16,950
for today's journey.

796
00:42:17,870 --> 00:42:19,040
Keep the decision to yourself only.

797
00:42:19,630 --> 00:42:20,390
I understand.

798
00:42:22,950 --> 00:42:24,800
Your poison technique is better than ever.

799
00:42:27,230 --> 00:42:28,120
This is newly made.

800
00:42:29,600 --> 00:42:30,870
Smash it at critical moment.

801
00:42:31,360 --> 00:42:32,670
It won't take any lives

802
00:42:33,080 --> 00:42:34,630
or hurt anyone physically,

803
00:42:35,280 --> 00:42:36,950
but even Great Masters

804
00:42:36,950 --> 00:42:38,080
will sleep quite a while from it.

805
00:42:39,000 --> 00:42:39,760
Thank you, Teacher!

806
00:42:39,840 --> 00:42:40,470
No problem.

807
00:42:41,520 --> 00:42:42,630
Just don't show off with it.

808
00:43:08,140 --> 00:43:11,460
In the river of history,

809
00:43:11,740 --> 00:43:14,660
time goes round and round.

810
00:43:18,020 --> 00:43:21,020
Memories about the former and present lives

811
00:43:21,380 --> 00:43:24,900
join each other in an endless way.

812
00:43:27,340 --> 00:43:29,500
In the long drunken Milky Way,

813
00:43:29,980 --> 00:43:32,220
one season follows another in a flash,

814
00:43:32,220 --> 00:43:34,420
and the wild geese are flying south.

815
00:43:34,740 --> 00:43:36,340
I just can't give up

816
00:43:36,340 --> 00:43:39,340
to be with you for my whole life.

817
00:43:39,700 --> 00:43:44,620
I have been hovering in the dreams
for hundreds and thousands of times.

818
00:43:46,420 --> 00:43:48,420
I can't even say a word when I watch the flowers falling.

819
00:43:49,260 --> 00:43:51,300
Year after year in the wandering,

820
00:43:51,300 --> 00:43:53,860
I count the remaining years.

821
00:43:53,980 --> 00:43:56,060
Even though we can't meet each other anymore,

822
00:43:56,180 --> 00:43:57,620
even though we have ended up the destiny,

823
00:43:58,460 --> 00:44:00,300
I never feel regretful.

